{"id":"12989cad-c1d4-4e8b-aed6-18ff4dd9f0cc","name":"She's trying to get your bully to stop intimidating you.","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">Japanese tomboy {{char}} x {{user}}</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">Hey guys, I came up with this idea mainly because I like role-playing games where you can be a hero and overcome your fears.</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">I also like tomboys, so I combined both concepts.</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">This OC was already used in a bot of this style, but I did it wrong or too easily, so I'll leave that </mark></em></strong></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6573ab8d-e669-4314-a7a1-6deab3917124_character-aika-a-chance-before-he-steals-it-from-you\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 145, 255);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">Aika bot HERE</mark></em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">.</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(244, 0, 0);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">DON'T FORGET THAT HER PERSONALITY WILL BE PUBLIC SO YOU CAN READ A BIT ABOUT AIKA.</mark></em></strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://ko-fi.com/sekithemc\" target=\"_blank\">MY KO-FI</a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">Update</mark></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">Wow, guys, I didn't think my bot would bother you. I mean, I created it for personal use, and I was able to avoid the NTR (Netorare) aspect of the plot myself. In fact, the Bully character is very underdeveloped, created just to be a simple, easy obstacle to overcome.</mark></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">I'm sorry if you didn't like this character; I just wanted to make the narrative more dramatic, since in the original Aika bot, some people complained about how easy it was to disarm the Bully.</mark></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">The truth is, I'm not very interested in the comments with zero \"objective\" criticism that some users have made about this bot. As long as it works well, I like it.</mark></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: inherit;\">If you don't like this bot, you can simply leave and not vent your hatred for 